commitment to bipartisanship,

00:03:55.100 --> 00:03:59.900
moral courage, public
service and civic engagement.

00:03:59.900 --> 00:04:02.820
We also celebrate tonight another
great American who believed

00:04:02.820 --> 00:04:05.440
in courage and civic engagement,

00:04:05.440 --> 00:04:09.310
President John F. Kennedy
