and Senator Inouye.

00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:22.110
It was also designed to honor
the special role of Hawaii

00:04:22.110 --> 00:04:24.180
in the development
of the Peace Corp.

00:04:24.180 --> 00:04:28.780 position:56%
