00:04:36.270 --> 00:04:40.540
of inspiring a sense of
service and idealism.

00:04:40.540 --> 00:04:42.570
They will highlight the
evolution of the Peace Corp,

00:04:42.570 --> 00:04:47.220
which was established by
President Kennedy on March 1, 1961,

00:04:47.220 --> 00:04:50.150
and discussed how it's ideals
remained relevant today,

00:04:50.150 --> 00:04:52.210
five decades later.

