getting a tour of Camp David

00:05:38.430 --> 00:05:41.390
from the then Attorney
General, Elliott Richardson,

00:05:41.390 --> 00:05:45.150
and noticing that Camp David
had Golden toilet seats.

00:05:45.150 --> 00:05:49.930
There were no such amenities
in Peace Corp, where he served

00:05:49.930 --> 00:05:53.630
from 1983 to 1985 after
attending Bowdoin College.

00:05:53.630 --> 00:05:57.280
He taught math in a high
school in Northwest Swaziland

00:05:57.280 --> 00:06:00.010
where there was no
electricity at all.

00:06:00.010 --> 00:06:02.690
But it could be said
that Netflix began there.

00:06:02.690 --> 00:06:06.070
He took his GRE exam in Swaziland.

00:06:06.070 --> 00:06:10.210
He was then admitted to Stanford's
program in computer science.

00:06:10.210 --> 00:06:12.480
He enjoyed a very successful
business career.

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:15.120
He created and sold
a software company,

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:18.930
always displaying the versatility
and self-reliance prized

00:06:18.930 --> 00:06:22.350
by the Peace Corp. That
background prepared him well

00:06:22.350 --> 00:06:25.330
for the day he received a
late fee from a video store

00:06:25.330 --> 00:06:28.480
after renting the moving Apollo 13.

00:06:28.480 --> 00:06:33.750
He was in fact six week's late
and owed $40 in on-the-spot.

00:06:33.750 --> 00:06:36.350
He decided to create a new
company for people who wanted

00:06:36.350 --> 00:06:39.920
to rent movies for
longer than one day.

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:43.960
Netflix was founded in 1997
as a DVD subscription service.

00:06:43.960 --> 00:06:48.470
Ten years later in 2007, it started
streaming content via the Internet.

00:06:48.470 --> 00:06:53.980
It now has over 100 million
members in over 190 countries,

00:06:53.980 --> 00:06:57.970
more than the population of
Germany, France, or England.

00:06:57.970 --> 00:07:00.620
Reed is an active educational
philanthropist.

00:07:00.620 --> 00:07:02.590
He served on the California
State Board

00:07:02.590 --> 00:07:05.350
of Education from 2000 to 2004.

00:07:05.350 --> 00:07:06.650
He is on the board

00:07:06.650 --> 00:07:09.180
of many educational organizations
including the California Charter

00:07:09.180 --> 00:07:13.330
