Learning, the KIPP Foundation,

00:07:13.330 --> 00:07:16.910
Pahara and the Hispanic
Foundation of Silicon Valley.

00:07:16.910 --> 00:07:19.440
He is also a board member of
Facebook and was on the board

00:07:19.440 --> 00:07:23.910
of Microsoft from 2007 to 2012.

00:07:23.910 --> 00:07:26.040
Our other panelist,
Secretary Elaine Chao,

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:29.760
is the 18th U.S. Secretary
of Transportation.

00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:32.750
At the age of eight, she
immigrated from Taiwan

00:07:32.750 --> 00:07:35.670
to the United States,
speaking no English.

00:07:35.670 --> 00:07:38.670
She graduated from high school
in New York, Mount Holyoke

00:07:38.670 --> 00:07:42.370
and Harvard Business School then
began a remarkable public career

00:07:42.370 --> 00:07:45.780
that has always given
inspiration to others.

00:07:45.780 --> 00:07:51.170
From 2001 to 2009, she was the
24th U.S. Secretary of Labor,

00:07:51.170 --> 00:07:53.370
the first Asian American
woman to be appointed

00:07:53.370 --> 00:07:55.830
to the Cabinet of American History.

00:07:55.830 --> 00:07:59.180 position:56%
Prior to that, she was the President
and CEO of United Way of America,

00:07:59.180 --> 00:08:02.590
and before that the Deputy
Secretary of Transportation.

00:08:02.590 --> 00:08:07.370
And she was the director of the
Peace Corp from 1991 to 1993,

00:08:07.370 --> 00:08:11.120
an eventful period in World history
and especially for the countries

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:13.360
in the former Soviet Union.

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:17.700
She was nominated for that post
by President George H. W. Bush,

00:08:17.700 --> 00:08:19.460
and during her tenure
she developed one

00:08:19.460 --> 00:08:23.150
of President Kennedy's original
ideas for the Peace Corp,

00:08:23.150 --> 00:08:26.190
which is that it should operate
in the Eastern European countries

00:08:26.190 --> 00:08:30.320
where development and
expression were often stifled.

00:08:30.320 --> 00:08:33.450
Under her leadership, the Peace
Corp expanded into Poland,

00:08:33.450 --> 00:08:37.290
Latvia, Lithuania, and Estonia.

