we also recognize as a need,

00:56:50.310 --> 00:56:54.800
it's only about seven percent of
50 plus, but we have a program

00:56:54.800 --> 00:56:57.400
for both called Peace Corp response

00:56:57.400 --> 00:57:02.130
where our short-term targeted
project based assignments

00:57:02.130 --> 00:57:05.100
that are sort of tailored
to people with experience

00:57:05.100 --> 00:57:07.830 position:56%
and generally those are older folks.

00:57:07.830 --> 00:57:12.660
So we are very open and welcoming
to people who are 50 plus.

00:57:12.660 --> 00:57:14.970
