would say is I think

00:58:52.570 --> 00:58:55.680
in the past Peace Corp would often
be sort of viewed as something

00:58:55.680 --> 00:58:59.500
that you sort of did
after college to get away

00:58:59.500 --> 00:59:01.790
and to have a great experience,

00:59:01.790 --> 00:59:04.400
but you were really
putting your career on hold.

00:59:04.400 --> 00:59:06.650
I think Peace Corp now
is a career accelerator.

00:59:06.650 --> 00:59:08.510
It always has been, but we've
really sort of in the 21st Century

00:59:08.510 --> 00:59:09.810
with the Internet and all
the different projects

00:59:09.810 --> 00:59:11.420
that volunteers are doing, there's
incredible benefits in terms

00:59:11.420 --> 00:59:12.890
of leadership development,
flexibility, adaptability,

00:59:12.890 --> 00:59:14.390
all the things that were mentioned,
and then we have benefits.

00:59:14.390 --> 00:59:15.690
