called the Fellows program.

00:59:18.290 --> 00:59:19.590
And then we also have a
readjustment allowance

00:59:19.590 --> 00:59:21.080
that helps them get started when
they reenter the United States.

00:59:21.080 --> 00:59:22.380
So we have lots of benefits
that would serve them.

